snippet.title: EVE ONLINE - Zenith Quadrant 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
EVE Online's Quadrant 3 is called "Zenith", and its arrival today will see the seismic reshaping of New Eden come to pass! Start playing EVE for free at https://bit.ly/play_eve

The final chapter of the Invasion story arc will come to an end as the Triglavians' plans approach their climactic conclusion, and Capsuleers will have a huge part to play in the star-spanning consequences of that reshaping. There will be visual updates, meta changes, login campaigns, events and more! 

Music & Sound Design: Makewaves Audio
